data.description: OPEN HOUSE  Saturday 12/9 from 11-1.  Welcome home!  Updated 1790 sq ft, 3/1 with a 1/1 converted garage ADU plus a large enclosed attached sunroom not counted in the sq footage.  Roof, exterior stucco, and appliances all new within the last 5 years and sunroom carpet, interior paint, countertops all just completed.  If that's not enough there is a 25x40 shop with 220v out back, mature fruit and nut trees and plenty of parking! Live in one/rent the other?  The possibilities are endless with this one!  Come see for yourself!
